h1. props

h2. Purpose

Provide additional custom properties.

h2. Examples

bc.
class SampleGriffonAddon {
    def props = [
        priority: [
            get: { /\* return some value \*/ },
            set: { v -> /\* store value \*/ }
        ]
    ]
}

h2. Description

The @props@ property is responsible for adding new properties to builders. Each property is defined as a pair of closures that function as setter and getter.
